ASHRAE Task Force

The worldwide building sector accounts for about 40% of energy-related carbon emissions and buildings remain a major sector that lacks sufficient mitigation policies. ASHRAE recognizes that our long-standing initiatives in energy efficiency should be expanded to building decarbonization.

Handbook

New Members and Associate Members receive a 12 month complimentary subscription to the Handbook Online, which includes access to the most recent 4 volumes of the Handbook
Once you submit payment, you can choose your membership benefit and additional product purchases.
Participants in the Developing Countries program receive a PDF version of the Handbook each June.

Due to the cost of printing and shipping the printed Handbook and for purposes of sustainability, ASHRAE encourages you to consider selecting the “Handbook Online plus PDF” option.
